WEBVTT

00:07.094 --> 00:10.271
MAN:
Good evening my dear
friends of Minston County.

00:10.358 --> 00:14.840
As we continue in this
fortunate year of 1946,

00:14.927 --> 00:17.800
I am delighted in the moral
leadership of our very own

00:17.887 --> 00:22.631
Mr. Bascum, for he is laboring
to mend the degenerate among us,

00:22.718 --> 00:26.200
from those who seek to
deaden the mind on narcotics,

00:26.287 --> 00:28.550
to the women of our town,
who degrade themselves through

00:28.637 --> 00:31.161
the sale of their bodies.

00:31.248 --> 00:34.512
Of pioneering treatments,
Mr. Bascum is bringing an era

00:34.599 --> 00:37.515
of ethical prosperity
to Minston,

00:37.602 --> 00:40.562
through a series of severe and
humane procedures re--.

00:40.649 --> 00:44.653
♪ [solemn music]

00:55.533 --> 00:57.100
BOY:
Why you sweating, mom?

00:57.187 --> 00:59.407
WOMAN:
One drop's
not sweating, Donnie.

00:59.494 --> 01:00.930
BOY:
You scared?

01:01.017 --> 01:02.714
WOMAN:
Will you
quit diggin' on me?

01:02.801 --> 01:04.063
I'm fine.

01:08.851 --> 01:12.115
[car squeaks]

01:16.685 --> 01:20.428
[♪♪♪]

01:20.515 --> 01:22.691
BOY:
What is this place?

01:22.777 --> 01:27.478
Oh gee, you ain't takin' me
to the orphan hole, are ya?

01:27.565 --> 01:29.524
WOMAN:
Who gave you a chicken
brained idea like that?

01:29.611 --> 01:32.875
BOY:
The round man that
comes over on Tuesdays,

01:32.962 --> 01:35.312
said he'd take me there if
I told anyone he was

01:35.399 --> 01:37.358
in our house.

01:37.445 --> 01:40.709
And if he does, I'll
pretend to be asleep,

01:40.795 --> 01:42.319
and when he comes
into my room,

01:42.406 --> 01:44.582
I'll jump up and poke
him in the belly with--.

01:44.669 --> 01:46.715
WOMAN:
Hell!

01:46.801 --> 01:49.196
What have I told you to do
with wicked thoughts like that?

01:49.283 --> 01:51.241
Huh?
Look at me.

01:51.328 --> 01:53.634
You feel 'em coming
you shoo 'em away.

01:53.722 --> 01:56.681
You keep shooin'
until they're gone.

01:56.768 --> 01:57.769
You hear me?

01:57.856 --> 01:59.684
Gone.

01:59.771 --> 02:02.513
[♪♪♪]

02:04.863 --> 02:06.082
WOMAN:
[sighs]

02:07.475 --> 02:09.128
[door opens]

02:30.846 --> 02:31.890
[door shuts]

02:31.977 --> 02:34.241
[footsteps]

02:34.328 --> 02:35.677
[door opens]

02:39.115 --> 02:41.465
WOMAN:
Hey.

02:41.552 --> 02:48.603
So, uh, when I get done,
I got a surprise for you.

02:48.690 --> 02:50.474
BOY:
What is it?

02:50.561 --> 02:52.737
WOMAN:
Gonna sleep
somewhere special tonight.

02:52.824 --> 02:54.913
BOY:
Mr Harold's Hotel?

02:55.000 --> 02:57.567
WOMAN:
Mmhmm.

02:57.655 --> 03:00.092
But you gotta watch your
sister for me, 'kay?

03:00.180 --> 03:02.617
Like a good big brother.

03:04.793 --> 03:08.449
Read your book until
you fall asleep.

03:08.536 --> 03:09.928
Okay.

03:10.015 --> 03:15.891
♪ [solemn music]

03:15.978 --> 03:16.978
WOMAN:
I love you.

03:17.066 --> 03:18.546
BOY:
I love you, too.

03:22.158 --> 03:24.943
[door squeaks and shuts]

03:25.030 --> 03:28.686
WOMAN:
[heavy breathing]

03:28.773 --> 03:30.514
[metal door rattling open]

03:33.648 --> 03:34.997
[door bangs shut]

03:35.084 --> 03:38.261
♪ [tense music] ♪

03:38.348 --> 03:46.051
[footsteps]

03:46.138 --> 03:53.972
[heavy breathing]

03:54.886 --> 04:02.938
♪ [tense music]

04:21.478 --> 04:29.486
[rattling footsteps
approaching]

04:34.143 --> 04:36.276
MAN:
Hello, Barbara.

04:38.016 --> 04:40.236
BARBARA:
Mr. Bascum.

04:40.323 --> 04:43.979
BASCUM:
I'm delighted that
you agreed to this over

04:44.066 --> 04:47.112
traditional consequences.

04:47.199 --> 04:49.201
BARBARA:
You think
it's gonna help me?

04:49.289 --> 04:54.250
BASCUM:
The clinicians
are quite hopeful.

04:54.337 --> 04:58.080
I of course value their
treatment process,

04:58.167 --> 05:03.433
but I'm placing most of
my faith in you, Barbara.

05:03.520 --> 05:07.611
Imagine your life no longer
defined by your

05:07.698 --> 05:11.702
vulgar behavior.

05:11.789 --> 05:16.707
A world where your children
are no longer tarnished

05:16.794 --> 05:19.623
by your reputation.

05:19.710 --> 05:26.935
Or Heaven forbid, relegated
to the care of the County.

05:27.022 --> 05:33.463
This is not a punishment to
atone for what you have done.

05:33.550 --> 05:39.207
It's an opportunity to
reimagine what you might become.

05:41.689 --> 05:48.609
[slow footsteps retreat]

05:48.696 --> 05:54.092
BARBARA:
[gasping]

05:55.920 --> 05:57.748
BASCUM:
Shall we?

06:05.887 --> 06:08.411
[wrapper crinkling]

06:19.553 --> 06:26.908
[♪♪♪]

06:41.444 --> 06:43.228
MAN:
Alton, would you please
apply the nodes to the

06:43.315 --> 06:46.406
subject's primary
pleasure sensories.

06:50.714 --> 06:54.283
[♪♪♪]

07:01.464 --> 07:04.859
MAN:
Please bring in the
erotic stimuli.

07:04.946 --> 07:09.254
Douglas, you may
step forward.

07:12.475 --> 07:14.390
MAN:
Please remove
your covering.

07:17.132 --> 07:18.438
[bang]

07:21.702 --> 07:22.616
[bang]

