[bang]

08:00.175 --> 08:02.046
MAN:
[indistinct]

08:02.133 --> 08:03.570
[bang]

08:03.657 --> 08:05.136
MAN:
He is but a creature.

08:05.223 --> 08:06.268
[bang]

08:06.355 --> 08:13.493
BARBARA:
[screaming]

08:17.714 --> 08:20.369
BASCUM:
I don't think
you're supposed to be here.

08:20.456 --> 08:24.591
♪ [ominous music]

08:24.678 --> 08:25.896
BARBARA:
Why?

08:25.983 --> 08:29.465
[crunching]

08:29.552 --> 08:30.727
BRENTON:
Donnie, Donnie, hey!

08:30.814 --> 08:32.076
Hey hey, enough.

08:32.163 --> 08:34.861
Alright?

08:34.948 --> 08:36.602
DONNIE:
You come near my
sister again and I'll make you

08:36.690 --> 08:40.302
