what's tried and tested.

17:27.133 --> 17:29.744
DONNIE:
She needs someone who
understands her to treat her.

17:29.831 --> 17:32.138
WOMAN:
Well, unless you
win the sweepstakes,

17:32.225 --> 17:35.576
