with any meat on your platter.

19:06.841 --> 19:10.671
DONNIE:
Maybe it'd be
better if the bomb did drop.

19:10.758 --> 19:12.499
BRENTON:
You don't mean that.

19:12.586 --> 19:14.414
DONNIE:
If I were you I'd move
back to Dakota and get on

19:14.501 --> 19:15.632
